  "slug": "what-bold-actions-have-i-been-delaying-journal",
  "title": "What bold actions have I been delaying",
  "subtitle": "A journal set for identifying where overthinking has replaced forward movement.",
  "excerpt": "A journal prompt set from Day 44 of the MONEY program. The prompts trace the specific actions that have been stalled by fear of the wrong move.",
  "type": "PRACTICE",
  "sourceNotes": "Adapted from Day 44 of The Money Journal: 12 Weeks to Peace, Freedom and Overflow (Rebecca J Page, 2025).",
  "body": {
    "type": "doc",
    "content": [
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "A journal set from Day 44 of the MONEY program. The prompts don't require you to take the action. They ask you to name what's in the way of it.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "New to journalling as a practice? Read ",
            "type": "text"
          },
          {
            "text": "journal prompts as practice",
            "type": "text",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "link",
                "attrs": {
                  "href": "/mindset/journal-prompts-as-practice"
                }
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "text": " first.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "The practice",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 3
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Warm-up",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 4
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Where are you right now with taking bold action around money?",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Write a paragraph. No assessment required, just a report from where you are today.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 4
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Think of a time you took bold action around money and it worked out. What did that feel like?",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Write what you remember. Concrete details count more than the feelings here.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 3
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Closer in",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 4
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "What actions around money, work, or investment have you been delaying?",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "List them. Don't justify why.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 4
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "What are you afraid might happen if you move forward?",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Write the actual fear, not the polished version. \"I'm afraid I'll look stupid\" is more useful than \"I'm not sure it's the right time.\"",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 4
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "What one action could you take today, however small, that moves you forward on one of those?",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Write it. Then write when you will do it.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Where this practice comes from",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Adapted from Day 44 of The Money Journal: 12 Weeks to Peace, Freedom and Overflow (Rebecca J Page, 2025).",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  },
